NOTICE — modifications to ansible-core
======================================

This repository is a MODIFIED version of ansible-core
(https://github.com/ansible/ansible), based on version 2.22.0.dev0.

It has been modified so that the Ansible controller (the side that runs
`ansible-playbook` and the other CLIs) can run natively on Microsoft Windows,
without WSL, Cygwin, or a Linux VM. The modifications were made in 2026.

This is an UNOFFICIAL fork. It is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or supported
by the Ansible project or Red Hat, Inc. "Ansible" is a trademark of Red Hat, Inc.

A summary of every change is in CHANGES_WINDOWS.md; the technical rationale and a
guide for re-porting future Ansible versions are in PORTING.md (English) and
PORTING_JP.md (日本語). The original upstream README is preserved as
README.upstream.md.

